      "side": 1,
      "message": "DCHECK or CHECK? Given the most likely motivation I can see for doing this, I think a CHECK makes more sense. But I’m wondering what else might have motivated this that would prompt the selection of DCHECK instead.",
      "revId": "11f748b78f9200d3e5cdd96b90c5d7704851a6bd",
